# features/products.feature

Feature: Product management

  Scenario: Create a new product
    Given a product exists with name "Test Product" and price 100
    When I update the product "Test Product" to have price 150
    Then the product "Test Product" should have price 150

  Scenario: Delete a product
    Given a product exists with name "Old Product" and price 50
    When I delete the product "Old Product"
    Then the product "Old Product" should no longer exist

  Scenario: Search for products by category
    Given a product exists with name "Product A" and category "Electronics"
    When I search for products by category "Electronics"
    Then the product "Product A" should be in the results
